@NODE NewSecure "The new security Features ..."

            Now its possible to hide the Crypter completely ...
                            Let us explain how:

	There are two ways to run the patch:


1. via startup-sequence (not sure)
   (for people with NO system knowledge)

	- add the line EnigmaII <DevName>: to your startup-sequence

	- Remember: Enigma only asks for the Password if you
		    PRESS THE LEFT MOUSEBUTTON WHILE BOOTING !!!  

	- rename the Files EnigmaRun, EnigmaII, WaitForCrypter
	  and CrypteActive if you want

2. after executing the startup-sequence

	- type "exelink enigmarun <anyCommand> <newname>"

	where <anyCommand> an executable File of your choice,
	and <newname> a new name of your choice for these two
	files is.

	What happens ?

	-if you start <newname> without CLI-Parameters, the <anyCommand>
	 will be executed
		
	-if you start <newname> with any CLI-Parameters, the <anyCommand>
 	 will be executed (with these Parameters)

	-if you start <newname> with "rmd" as first CLI Parameter, 
	 enigmarun will be executed 

	Example:

	"exelink enigmarun dir Ndir"
	<Files are now linked together>

	"Ndir" 
	<Current Directory is shown>

	"Ndir dh0:"
	<Directory of dh0: is shown>

	"Ndir rmd dh0:"
	<A requester aks you for the PW for dh0:>

	-you can change the string "rmd" with a FileMon ... search and
	 replace it with your favorite 3 chars in Enigmarun

	-pack the linked Files using Powerpacker or so

	-no one will find your Enigmarun ... hehehhehe 

	- Remember: after running your "Enigmarun", you need a "Diskchange"
	
	- You don`t need the EnigmaII - Skript anymore



	...... Means .....

	Enigmarun will only launch if either the left Mousebutton 
	is pressed or the correct first CLI-Parameter is entered


	... now ... use your imagination (you can i.e. use the second
	way of installing in your startup-sequence) 
	change the EnigmaII-Batchfile, if you want, protect your System
	as good as possible.



	And we have a special offer for the real Elite only:

	We compile a special Version of the Enigma II Project, which
	meets exactly your needs (another key to activate Enigmarun,
	a different way of crypting, special security features, like
	an emergency-password (formats HD if entered, you can give this 
	PW to the cops, if they aks hehehe), Hotlinesupport an so on ...

	... for only 50 US-Dollars  

		Contact us, if you can !
@ENDNODE
